+++ b/final/components/magicui/morphing-text.tsx

-The original component used a CSS blur+opacity technique with two <span>
-elements and requestAnimationFrame loop. No SVG paths, no font parsing,
-no interpolation — just cross-fade with motion blur.

+Replaced with SVG path interpolation engine:
+  - opentype.js font loading → SVG path extraction
+  - Path resampling + centroid alignment + lerp interpolation
+  - Spring physics via motion/react useSpring
+  - Catmull-Rom → Cubic Bézier smooth output
+  - Adaptive performance sentinel (auto-downgrade on frame budget exceeded)
+  - Hover and auto-cycle trigger modes
+  - onMorphComplete callback
+  - SSR-safe with next/dynamic + font error recovery

 Key additions in interface:
+  fontSize?: number
+  precision?: Precision
+  trigger?: "auto" | "hover"
+  interval?: number
+  fontUrl?: string
+  stiffness?: number
+  damping?: number
+  restDelta?: number
+  hoverToIndex?: number
+  fill?: string
+  smooth?: boolean
+  letterSpacing?: number
+  onMorphComplete?: (settledIndex: number) => void

