+Core geometry pipeline for morphing text:
+
+ Types:
+   Point, SubPath, ParsedPath, Precision
+
+ SVG Path Parser:
+   parseSvgPath(d) → PathCommand[]
+   commandsToRawSubPaths(commands) → SubPath[]
+
+ Flatten (Bézier → polyline):
+   flattenSubPath() with recursive midpoint subdivision (max depth 8)
+   flattenCubic(), flattenQuad() with flatness test
+   cubicFlatness(), quadFlatness(), pointToLineDistance()
+
+ Resample (uniform arc-length):
+   computePerimeter(), resolveNumSamples(), resampleSubPath()
+   Dynamic mode: samplesPerUnit × perimeter, clamped to [minSamples, maxSamples]
+   Fixed mode: explicit numSamples
+
+ Centroid Alignment:
+   computeCentroid(), rotatePointsToNearest()
+   computeGlobalCentroid()
+
+ Multi-factor Sub-path Matching (Round 11):
+   computeSignedArea() — Shoelace formula for winding detection
+   computeArea(), isHole() — hole vs outline classification
+   SubPathDescriptor — centroid, area, relativeArea, isHole
+   buildDescriptors(), computeMatchCost() — winding penalty (2.0) + area
+     similarity (0.8) + position distance (0.5)
+   matchSubPathsByCentroid() — cost-sorted greedy matching
+
+ Ghost Path Padding:
+   createGhostSubPath() — zero-area path at centroid
+   createShrinkGhostSubPath() — for disappearing holes
+   findParentOutlineCentroid() — smallest containing outline's centroid
+   alignParsedPaths() — full alignment pipeline with winding-aware ghosts
+
+ Interpolation:
+   interpolatePaths(a, b, t) — lerp with clamping and defensive checks
+
+ Catmull-Rom Smoothing (Round 10):
+   CATMULL_ROM_TENSION = 0.5
+   catmullRomToBezier() — tangent estimation for cubic Bézier CPs
+   getPoint() — wrap/clamp for closed/open paths
+   smoothSubPathToD() — polyline → C commands
+   smoothPathToD() — ParsedPath → smooth SVG d string
+
+ SVG Output:
+   parsedPathToD() — linear (L) segments
+   smoothPathToD() — smooth cubic (C) segments
+
+ Public API:
+   flattenPath(), resamplePath(), preparePathsForMorph()

