+FontManager: opentype.js font loader with caching & SSR safety
+
+  FontManager class:
+    - Map cache for loaded fonts (no duplicate fetches)
+    - pending Map for concurrent request deduplication
+    - Dynamic import of opentype.js (avoids SSR bundling)
+    - Three-tier error recovery: remote → local → synthetic
+
+  _fetchAndParse(url):
+    - HTTP status check
+    - Local fallback for external URLs (/fonts/Inter-Regular.ttf)
+
+  _loadFallback():
+    - Try /fonts/Inter-Regular.ttf
+    - Last resort: create minimal opentype.js Font with notdef glyph
+
+  Singleton: getFontManager() — client-only creation
+
+  Convenience functions:
+    loadFont(url), loadFontFromBase64(base64)
+
+  Path extraction:
+    getCharPath(font, char, fontSize)
+    getTextPathWithSpacing(font, text, fontSize, letterSpacing)
+      — uses opentype.js font.getPath() with kerning + tracking
+    getTextPaths(font, text, fontSize)
+
+  DEFAULT_FONT_URL = "/fonts/Inter-Regular.ttf"

